    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An ISO standard developed to measure and calibrate lightfastness and fading of colorants and other materials. It consists of a card that contains eight sections of blue-dyed wool cloth, each with a different lightfastness. The dyes fade at a known rate. </Note_Text>
